title: Ep. 95 - The Multiverse
description: The boys really dove deep into a wormhole on this one. They discussed The Multiverse Theory, clean energy, and the westward expansion of America. This episode also features an I Want To Know segment, a gem of a listener question and Friday Bangerz.
